    <h1>Project Proposal</h1>
    <h2>What is your website about?</h2>
    <p>This website informs travelers about the city of Dubai! This includes dining option, night-life, attractions and different activities.</p>
    <br>
    <h2>What is the objective of your website? (Also read as why would this site be important?)</h2>
    <p>The objective is to let travelers know the different places they can visit in Dubai.</p>
    <br>
    <h2>Who is your target audience?</h2>
    <p>Travelers who are going to Dubai for the first time and want information on different restaurants and attractions.</p>
    <br>
    <h2>What content do you plan to include in each page of your website?</h2>
    <p>Links to the most famous dining options with picture, the best attractions to visit when it is hot, the best place to visit at night, the best malls to go to.</p>
